These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Game: whist, go
Music-Genre: blues, house
1. Music-Genre:blues is in an even position##4
2. Music-Genre:house == Game:go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Game   | go | whist |
| Music-Genre     | house    | blues   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Hobby: card-games, video-games
Transport: jet-ski, snowmobile
1. Transport:jet-ski is in an odd position##4
2. Hobby:video-games is on the left of Hobby:card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Hobby   | video-games | card-games        |
| Transport      | jet-ski  | snowmobile |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
